description:
What is #inflation, why is it happening, and what can governments do about it? We answer these questions in our newest series, Ask an Economist.
#askanexpert 

Send your questions to AskanEconomist@imf.org and we’ll answer them in our next episode.        
Read more about inflation: https://bit.ly/3Lo0lId
